sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 用户
    participant UI as Web UI
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant Agent as Foodie Agent
    participant Tools as Tool Calling
    User->>UI: 输入场景/人数/食材或商圈
    UI->>API: POST /api/foodie/start
    API->>Agent: 构造会话状态
    Agent->>Tools: 调用 Graph-RAG / 小红书 / 高德
    Tools-->>Agent: 返回候选与证据
    Agent-->>API: 输出推荐卡片与健康说明
    UI-->>User: 展示候选、详情、导出 PDF
